{"tid":387331,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係呢個社會已經生存到好攰","createTime":"2017-09-04T14:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T04:50:24.000Z","uid":35300,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e8380636189df0a6d82f7056c65b8ca5ec7586c","tid":387331,"uid":35300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:15:17.000Z","msg":"平時返工面對住好多壓力 已經好唔開心<br />\n自己朋友又唔多 平時已經感到好孤獨<br />\n但係又要戴住個假面具做人 唔可以畀人睇到自己失敗懦弱既一面<br />\n<br />\n每日最開心就係可以返到屋企可以打下機<br />\n但係又要比屋企人煩 話你成日掛住打機無出息 <br />\n呢一種人生入面高不成低不就嘅感覺好可怕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fa0de655d5d0c2edc0a1774bac3193c348d9e1","tid":387331,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己已經死咗，而家好似行屍走肉咁"},{"pid":"dabe364b91827dbce9666e922e0e4a3247547c8b","tid":387331,"uid":35300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f19c4fe84932aa053b58d47408af9489078566c7","tid":387331,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"生無可戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec722f6a27ef164d57d4d498614f5a1d16fa8697","tid":387331,"uid":124660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:21:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時返工面對住好多壓力 已經好唔開心<br />\n自己朋友又唔多 平時已經感到好孤獨<br />\n但係又要戴住個假面具做人 唔可以畀人睇到自己失敗懦弱既一面<br />\n<br />\n每日最開心就係可以返到屋企可以打下機<br />\n但係又要比屋企人煩 話你成日掛住打機無出息 <br />\n呢一種人生入面高不成低不就嘅感覺好可怕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有個知己傾下計打下機都已經足夠令自己撐落去，<br />\n平時返工返學既煩惱都會一掃而清<br />\n<br />\n可惜我無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(我都想有)"},{"pid":"501d2361877c35499e0b436ab58679a4e848b4b7","tid":387331,"uid":57634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ba756c7b2d7ac6b8980dd7b95c684280244b39","tid":387331,"uid":35300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:56:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時返工面對住好多壓力 已經好唔開心<br />\n自己朋友又唔多 平時已經感到好孤獨<br />\n但係又要戴住個假面具做人 唔可以畀人睇到自己失敗懦弱既一面<br />\n<br />\n每日最開心就係可以返到屋企可以打下機<br />\n但係又要比屋企人煩 話你成日掛住打機無出息 <br />\n呢一種人生入面高不成低不就嘅感覺好可怕<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有個知己傾下計打下機都已經足夠令自己撐落去，<br />\n平時返工返學既煩惱都會一掃而清<br />\n<br />\n可惜我無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(我都想有)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前都有一班朋友一齊打機<br />\n但係 最後有啲要結婚我話 有啲要返工<br />\n最後就冇咗一齊打機 連聯絡都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bad27ed32844099fcbfd7e8bc69d5b26426c3e7","tid":387331,"uid":35300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbacdf347e3004d3d110c327303e9b320bfd8aac","tid":387331,"uid":124660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉d輕鬆d既工囉一係，多d時間去發掘興趣&amp;識d同興趣既人，唔知你返工因咩愁(人事？工作量？)，我自己就鐘意選份輕鬆既工support自己既興趣，因為我興趣唔可以當飯食<br />\n(如果可以既話你係個好幸運既人)"},{"pid":"2f278867728323422d217f4eb6a5d195eaf1754d","tid":387331,"uid":124660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:29:19.000Z","msg":"雖然無知己(過客就好多)，但最小我依條路都算行得舒服過好多人，或者值得你考慮"},{"pid":"de45771e291be2c1ad615213245877fbee06b3b0","tid":387331,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"放工有時間做其他野已經算唔錯，<br />\n收工坐車食埋飯又夠鐘訓覺，<br />\n第二朝又迫車返工，唔知為乜"},{"pid":"b44f26a9abff9bc99a41087981ebf582674f9a83","tid":387331,"uid":117722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然無知己(過客就好多)，但最小我依條路都算行得舒服過好多人，或者值得你考慮</blockquote><br />\n有咩工輕鬆？每次都係一個火坑跳去另一個火坑"},{"pid":"8a641277ed1b54c22d6e74a688c7ec610dfd4113","tid":387331,"uid":35300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然無知己(過客就好多)，但最小我依條路都算行得舒服過好多人，或者值得你考慮</blockquote><br />\n有咩工輕鬆？每次都係一個火坑跳去另一個火坑</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707114cc1600371e4a4daf613d44bd0c95689678","tid":387331,"uid":35300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:21:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bdf304f73ec4faf9244f80ac92b1246cdf75ce","tid":387331,"uid":24299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:51:49.000Z","msg":"機械式嘅生活令人磨滅鬥志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb974675cc6f8ee2eed1639d7c71c5443888b9e","tid":387331,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T17:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>雖然無知己(過客就好多)，但最小我依條路都算行得舒服過好多人，或者值得你考慮</blockquote><br />\n有咩工輕鬆？每次都係一個火